* Themis Lazaridis: topology and parameters needed for MOBHY
* To be read after toppar_water_ions.str
*

read rtf card append
* Topology for hydronium, hydroxide etc
*
31  1

MASS  -1  HHH   1.00800 H  ! H3O+ HYDROGEN
MASS  -1  OXR   3.99940 O  ! For "ring" hydroxide
MASS  -1  OR    3.00000 O  ! For "ring" hydroxide
MASS  -1  DUM   0.00000 DUM! from stream/misc/toppar_dum_noble_gases.str.

default first none last none
AUTO ANGLE DIHE

RESI H3O          1.000 NOANG NODIH
GROUP
ATOM OH2  OT     -0.755
ATOM H1   HHH     0.585
ATOM H2   HHH     0.585
ATOM H3   HHH     0.585
BOND OH2 H1 OH2 H2 OH2 H3 H1 H2 H1 H3 H2 H3   
ANGLE H1 OH2 H2             ! required
ANGLE H1 OH2 H3             ! required
ANGLE H2 OH2 H3             ! required
DONOR H1 OH2
DONOR H2 OH2
DONOR H3 OH2
ACCEPTOR OH2
PATCHING FIRS NONE LAST NONE

RESI HOH         0.000 NOANG NODIH ! same as TIP3, use for protonated hydroxide
GROUP
ATOM OH2  OT     -0.834
ATOM H1   HT      0.417
ATOM H2   HT      0.417
BOND OH2 H1 OH2 H2 H1 H2    ! the last bond is needed for shake
ANGLE H1 OH2 H2             ! required
DONOR H1 OH2
DONOR H2 OH2
ACCEPTOR OH2
PATCHING FIRS NONE LAST NONE

END

